Author: floatlikeafeather-
Text: I do a meal plan and just eat 1/3 or 1/2 of the meals at a time bc that’s a calorie count I’m ok with. The meals are already in loseit so I can track my calories.
Not meals, per se, but check out Imperfect Produce!! Veggies delivered weekly on the cheap!  I just freeze w/e I'm not planning to eat that week + it's clutch for having safe snack foods on hand
